headline: Soybeans Continue Losses at Midday
summary: Soybeans are down 5 t 7 ¼ cents across most contracts at midday. There were 349 deliveries issued against August beans by the Bunge house account for first notice day. The cmdtyView national average Cash Bean price is down 9 1/4 cents at $9.21 ¾. Soymeal futures are showing gains...
